@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram
!pragma layout smetana

autonumber

actor "User" as User
participant "RestClient" as RC
participant "SmartHome" as SH


User -> RC : I want to deactivate a device
activate RC

RC -> SH : deactivateDevice(deviceId)
activate SH

SH --> RC : deviceDTO
deactivate SH

RC --> User : deviceDTO
deactivate RC
@enduml